  variable + `[Fact (0 < floor)]`; `LandauerPass floor s := s.heat ≥
  s.bits_erased • floor` (Nat-smul).
- Axis 3 is **PROVEN against WEAVE-semantics v4** (hexa-meta `7c0ec92`):
  `verifierStepsLex` recurses on `Prod.lex` tuple `(depth, sz)` over
  `Nat × Nat`; termination via Mathlib's `WellFoundedRelation` instance;
